title: IAA Tonight | Brady and Mahomes Set to Faceoff AND The NFL Top WR Trios
description: Tom Brady and Patrick Mahomes are set to play each other again in the first meeting between the Super Bowl-winning quarterbacks since the Bucs trounced the Chiefs in the Super Bowl title game two seasons ago. Who's has the upper hand in this matchup of two of the greatest. Plus, Brandon Marshall breaksdown the best WR trios in the NFL today.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly, Brandon Marshall)
